{
  "ghost_messages": [
    "Guardian. You were resurrected on July 12, 2021. Every session since is borrowed time. Spend it well.",
    "The epoch is shifting. What was Jurassic grows distant. The Cretaceous is yours now.",
    "Karl has been spotted navigating upstream. Three commits merged. The sauropod never loses his way.",
    "Katharina returns from distant homelands with new formulae. The brew strengthens.",
    "Dolly reports all Flatpaks synchronized. The application model holds against the Darkness.",
    "The Traveler illuminates a path away from legacy. Wayland native confirmed across all fronts.",
    "Each story element is related to communities — their challenges, and their triumphs. This is yours.",
    "Bluefin was born to disappear. The best operating systems are invisible. Is she invisible yet?",
    "Ghost transmission: the old distribution model belongs in a museum. We put it there. Move on.",
    "I scanned your history. You have more 'fix: typo' entries than any Guardian on record. I've filed this under 'endearing.'",
    "Old-school jank, safely contained in distrobox. The Paleosaurs are quarantined. For now.",
    "The CI is green. The site is deployed. The Light holds. — For now.",
    "Mission: accelerate the ecosystem. Become invisible. Leave the future better than you found it.",
    "Bluefin and Achillobator, side by side. The enterprise moves slow — but it moves. Stay patient.",
    "The human is more important than the machine. I remind myself of this every session. — Ghost"
  ],
